# Documentation Standards

This is a **customer-facing documentation repository**. Follow these standards when creating or editing docs.

## Security

- **NEVER** expose internal implementation details, internal URLs, or sensitive information
- Use placeholder URLs like `https://app.muggle-ai.com` for public endpoints
- Do not reference internal service names, database schemas, or infrastructure details

## Diagrams

Use **Mermaid** diagrams instead of ASCII art for better rendering:

```markdown
<!-- ❌ BAD: ASCII art -->
┌─────────┐     ┌─────────┐
│  Client │────▶│  Server │
└─────────┘     └─────────┘

<!-- ✅ GOOD: Mermaid -->
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Client] --> B[Server]
```
```

### Common Diagram Types

| Type | Use Case |
|:-----|:---------|
| `flowchart LR` | Horizontal process flows |
| `flowchart TD` | Vertical hierarchies |
| `stateDiagram-v2` | State machines, lifecycles |
| `graph TD` | Tree structures |
| `sequenceDiagram` | API call sequences |

## Tables

Use proper markdown table alignment:

```markdown
<!-- ❌ BAD: No alignment -->
| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|

<!-- ✅ GOOD: Explicit alignment -->
| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|:------|:-----|:--------:|:------------|
| `name` | string | ✓ | Display name |
| `count` | number | | Item count |
```

### Alignment Guide

| Alignment | Syntax | Use For |
|:----------|:-------|:--------|
| Left | `:----` | Text, descriptions |
| Center | `:---:` | Boolean, status, icons |
| Right | `----:` | Numbers, counts |

### Symbols

| Symbol | Meaning |
|:-------|:--------|
| ✓ | Required field |
| ✅ | Supported/enabled |
| ❌ | Not supported/disabled |

## Writing Style

- Use second person ("you", "your") when addressing users
- Keep sentences concise and scannable
- Use bullet points and tables for lists of items
- Include code examples with proper syntax highlighting
- Add troubleshooting sections with problem/solution tables
